title: 586 Holly - Garden Level 2BR // SEPTEMBER
posting_body: ['2-BR apartment --', 'Available September', '586 Holly, St Paul, MN 55102 -- Garden Level; $1,170/mo', 'Available for a September move in', 'Two blocks north of Summit Ave (three blocks north of Grand Ave),', '1/2-block east of Dale St, you are close to the many shops and scenic areas St. Paul has to offer.', ' #GreatForMitchellStudents #GreatForMitchellHamlineStudents', 'Our unit features:', '- Approx 700 sq ft.', '- 2-BR, LR, Kitchen, Bath (no formal dining room)', '- Hardwood floors', '- Owner pays radiator heat, water, trash, and stove gas', '- Corner apartment.', ' Garden level = look out windows at the grass/snow.', '- Laundry and storage available in building next door', '-- Great lease terms!', 'Flexible or Fixed.', 'Quoted rents are for a 9-12 month fixed term lease.', 'Additional $25/mo for flexible term.', '- Free off-street parking lot (space is limited)', '- Smoke-Free!!', ' All leases prohibit smoking, candles, and incense anywhere inside the building or on the property outside.', '- Advertised price is for 1 or 2 people.', ' Additional resident would be an extra $75/month fee.', ' Maximum of 3 residents.', '** We are a family run business, not a big management company, who really cares for our buildings and the tenants so you will receive personal attention and care if you choose to rent from us.', ' Thanks!!', 'For more information, please contact the property managers directly and reference this CL ad:', 'Alisa or Brenna', 'Day:', 'show contact info', 'Evening:', 'show contact info', 'Email:  see craigslist "reply to" link at top of this ad', 'Website for more information:', 'http://www.apts.cc', 'This 2BR APARTMENT is for rent at 586 Holly, Saint Paul, Minnesota 55102']
